snippet.title: Rivals 2 Kragg Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Kragg is the latest character revealed for the Rivals 2 launch roster in 2024! See the legend of Kragg along with brand new gameplay in this character reveal trailer. Learn more about Rivals 2 at https://rivals2.com
